"title": "8126: guidance, need for God's",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8126",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God's guidance is needed because people are naturally ignorant and rebellious and there are many who lead others astray.</p>\n<h2>The need to know and do the will of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:23\">JER 10:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:18\">EZR 7:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:3\">1TH 4:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:20-Heb13:21\">HEB 13:20–13:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:15\">1PE 2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:17\">1JN 2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:10\">MAT 6:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:21\">MAT 7:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:50\">MAT 12:50</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:35\">MRK 3:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:21\">LUK 8:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:17\">JHN 7:17</a></p>\n<h3>The concern of Jesus Christ to do the will of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:38\">JHN 6:38</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:34\">JHN 4:34</a></p>\n<h2>By themselves people are ignorant of the right way in life</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:12\">PRO 14:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl6:12\">ECC 6:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:7\">ECC 8:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:6\">ISA 53:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:10\">ISA 59:10</a> <em>blindness the result of disobedience</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:36\">MAT 9:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:25\">1PE 2:25</a></p>\n<h2>Warnings against false guidance</h2>\n<h3>False prophets and teachers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:25-Jer23:27\">JER 23:25–23:27</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:52\">LUK 11:52</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:13\">MAT 23:13</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:16\">ISA 9:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:13\">JER 23:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer27:9-Jer27:10\">JER 27:9–27:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:5\">MIC 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:1-2Pet2:3\">2PE 2:1–2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:17-Jude1:19\">JUD 1:17–1:19</a></p>\n<h3>False shepherds and guides</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:6\">JER 50:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:24\">MAT 24:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:12\">ISA 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:21\">JER 10:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:1-Jer23:2\">JER 23:1–23:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:4-Ezek34:6\">EZK 34:4–34:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:14\">MAT 15:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:30\">ACT 20:30</a></p>\n<h3>Idols and mediums</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech10:2\">ZEC 10:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:31\">LEV 19:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:22-Isa41:24\">ISA 41:22–41:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:4\">AMO 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:19\">HAB 2:19</a></p>\n<h3>Other agencies</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:3\">1KI 11:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:9\">2KI 21:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr21:11\">2CH 21:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:29\">PRO 16:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:33\">1CO 15:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:9\">REV 12:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:23\">REV 18:23</a></p>\n<h2>Despite knowing God's will, sinners still rebel against him</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:11-Jer18:12\">JER 18:11–18:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:9-Isa30:11\">ISA 30:9–30:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:16\">JER 6:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer42:5-Jer42:6\">JER 42:5–42:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer42:19-Jer42:21\">JER 42:19–42:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:3\">2TI 4:3</a></p>\n<h2>The adverse consequences of false guidance and disobedience</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr10:13-1Chr10:14\">1CH 10:13–10:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:12\">JOB 5:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:10-Ps33:11\">PSA 33:10–33:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps146:3-Ps146:4\">PSA 146:3–146:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:3\">ISA 19:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:1\">ISA 30:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer19:7\">JER 19:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:5-Hos11:7\">HOS 11:5–11:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:7-Heb3:11\">HEB 3:7–3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:7-Ps95:11\">PSA 95:7–95:11</a></p>",
